    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2021 Honda Accord in fair condition. The interior shows noticeable wear on upholstery and trim, including staining and scuffing in high-use areas. Controls and displays are functional. The exterior has visible scratches and minor dents consistent with regular use. Mechanically sound with no major issues, but this vehicle has seen moderate use and shows it.",
      "price": 16000.0,
